simulator.runner

Class CompanySimulatorRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • simulator.runner.CompanySimulatorRunner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class CompanySimulatorRunner
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    This runnable simulates a company's production and delivery chain based on the given economy simulator metrics. The base unit of this runnable is 1 second. This means that 1 execution of the method run is equivalent to 1 second elapsed in real time.
    Since:
    1.0
